International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
Date: Fri, 15 Aug 2002 06:37:52 -0700 (PDT)
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: WHO WER Notifications received from 8 to 14 Aug 2003 [edited]
<http://www.who.int/wer/2003/wer7833/en/>

Weekly Epidemiological Record notifications report 1 imported case of
cholera in the USA noted during 2-11 Jun 2003.
--
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[The risk of the spread of cholera in the USA is quite low because the
sanitation systems are good. But ProMED-mail would like to receive details
of the origin and type of cholera, as this would be valuable information
for public health officials everywhere. - Mod.LL]
